		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-jvt3tha",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-jvt3tha"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "Debug 网络质量的时候，我们一般会关注两个因素：延迟和吞吐量（带宽）。延迟比较好验证，Ping 一下或者 mtr"
				},
				{
					"Type": "NodeSup",
					"Data": "sup",
					"Children": [
						{
							"Type": "NodeSupOpenMarker"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeText",
							"Data": "[1]"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeSupCloseMarker"
						}
					]
				},
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": " 一下就能看出来。这篇文章分享一个 debug 吞吐量的办法。"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-k11x7a8",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-k11x7a8"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "看重吞吐量的场景一般是所谓的长肥管道(Long Fat Networks, LFN, rfc7323 "
				},
				{
					"Type": "NodeSup",
					"Data": "sup",
					"Children": [
						{
							"Type": "NodeSupOpenMarker"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeText",
							"Data": "[2]"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeSupCloseMarker"
						}
					]
				},
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": " ). 比如下载大文件。吞吐量没有达到网络的上限，主要可能受 3 个方面的影响："
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-f2q3vlm",
			"Type": "NodeList",
			"ListData": {
				"Typ": 1
			},
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-f2q3vlm"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"ID": "20220901143215-s9jg826",
					"Type": "NodeListItem",
					"ListData": {
						"Typ": 1,
						"Delimiter": 46,
						"Marker": "MS4=",
						"Num": 1
					},
					"Properties": {
						"id": "20220901143215-s9jg826"
					},
					"Children": [
						{
							"ID": "20220901143215-1w7razg",
							"Type": "NodeParagraph",
							"Properties": {
								"id": "20220901143215-1w7razg"
							},
							"Children": [
								{
									"Type": "NodeText",
									"Data": "发送端出现了瓶颈"
								}
							]
						}
					]
				},
				{
					"ID": "20220901143215-dpitu2v",
					"Type": "NodeListItem",
					"ListData": {
						"Typ": 1,
						"Delimiter": 46,
						"Marker": "Mi4=",
						"Num": 2
					},
					"Properties": {
						"id": "20220901143215-dpitu2v"
					},
					"Children": [
						{
							"ID": "20220901143215-fcxm1a2",
							"Type": "NodeParagraph",
							"Properties": {
								"id": "20220901143215-fcxm1a2"
							},
							"Children": [
								{
									"Type": "NodeText",
									"Data": "接收端出现了瓶颈"
								}
							]
						}
					]
				},
				{
					"ID": "20220901143215-bw398fc",
					"Type": "NodeListItem",
					"ListData": {
						"Typ": 1,
						"Delimiter": 46,
						"Marker": "My4=",
						"Num": 3
					},
					"Properties": {
						"id": "20220901143215-bw398fc"
					},
					"Children": [
						{
							"ID": "20220901143215-on1ip4i",
							"Type": "NodeParagraph",
							"Properties": {
								"id": "20220901143215-on1ip4i"
							},
							"Children": [
								{
									"Type": "NodeText",
									"Data": "中间的网络层出现了瓶颈"
								}
							]
						}
					]
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-na3n7vs",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-na3n7vs"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "发送端出现瓶颈一般的情况是 buffer 不够大，因为发送的过程是，应用调用 syscall，将要发送的数据放到 buffer 里面，然后由系统负责发送出去。如果 buffer 满了，那么应用会阻塞住（如果使用 block 的 API 的话），直到 buffer 可用了再继续 write，生产者和消费者模式。"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-bj12536",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-bj12536"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeImage",
					"Data": "span",
					"Children": [
						{
							"Type": "NodeBang"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeOpenBracket"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeLinkText",
							"Data": "图片"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeCloseBracket"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeOpenParen"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeLinkDest",
							"Data": "assets/640-20220901143214-ilftwd5"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeCloseParen"
						}
					]
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-a7p8c14",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-a7p8c14"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "发送端出现瓶颈一般都比较好排查，甚至通过应用的日志看何时阻塞住了即可。大部分情况都是第 2，3 种情况，比较难以排查。这种情况发生在，发送端的应用已经将内容写入到了系统的 buffer 中，但是系统并没有很快的发送出去。"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-r4gx07a",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-r4gx07a"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "TCP 为了优化传输效率（注意这里的传输效率，并不是单纯某一个 TCP 连接的传输效率，而是整体网络的效率），会:"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-gy754np",
			"Type": "NodeList",
			"ListData": {
				"Typ": 1
			},
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-gy754np"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"ID": "20220901143215-xhxp052",
					"Type": "NodeListItem",
					"ListData": {
						"Typ": 1,
						"Delimiter": 46,
						"Marker": "MS4=",
						"Num": 1
					},
					"Properties": {
						"id": "20220901143215-xhxp052"
					},
					"Children": [
						{
							"ID": "20220901143215-r8g92i1",
							"Type": "NodeParagraph",
							"Properties": {
								"id": "20220901143215-r8g92i1"
							},
							"Children": [
								{
									"Type": "NodeText",
									"Data": "保护接收端，发送的数据不会超过接收端的 buffer 大小 (Flow control)。数据发送到接受端，也是和上面介绍的过程类似，kernel 先负责收好包放到 buffer 中，然后上层应用程序处理这个 buffer 中的内容，如果接收端的 buffer 过小，那么很容易出现瓶颈，即应用程序还没来得及处理就被填满了。那么如果数据继续发过来，buffer 存不下，接收端只能丢弃。"
								}
							]
						}
					]
				},
				{
					"ID": "20220901143215-4p8oq7w",
					"Type": "NodeListItem",
					"ListData": {
						"Typ": 1,
						"Delimiter": 46,
						"Marker": "Mi4=",
						"Num": 2
					},
					"Properties": {
						"id": "20220901143215-4p8oq7w"
					},
					"Children": [
						{
							"ID": "20220901143215-c4pf0vx",
							"Type": "NodeParagraph",
							"Properties": {
								"id": "20220901143215-c4pf0vx"
							},
							"Children": [
								{
									"Type": "NodeText",
									"Data": "保护网络，发送的数据不会 overwhelming 网络 (Congestion Control, 拥塞控制), 如果中间的网络出现瓶颈，会导致长肥管道的吞吐不理想；"
								}
							]
						}
					]
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-ckxd2aj",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-ckxd2aj"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "对于接收端的保护，在两边连接建立的时候，会协商好接收端的 buffer 大小 (receiver window size, rwnd), 并且在后续的发送中，接收端也会在每一个 ack 回包中报告自己剩余和接受的 window 大小。这样，发送端在发送的时候会保证不会发送超过接收端 buffer 大小的数据。（意思是，发送端需要负责，receiver 没有 ack 的总数，不会超过 receiver 的 buffer.）"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-doao7w7",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-doao7w7"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeImage",
					"Data": "span",
					"Children": [
						{
							"Type": "NodeBang"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeOpenBracket"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeLinkText",
							"Data": "图片"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeCloseBracket"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeOpenParen"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeLinkDest",
							"Data": "assets/640-20220901143214-q5kxwk9"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeCloseParen"
						}
					]
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-nshugha",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-nshugha"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "对于网络的保护，原理也是维护一个 Window，叫做 Congestion window，拥塞窗口，cwnd, 这个窗口就是当前网络的限制，发送端不会发送超过这个窗口的容量（没有 ack 的总数不会超过 cwnd）。"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-465hjla",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-465hjla"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "怎么找到这个 cwnd 的值呢？"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-b16bs2m",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-b16bs2m"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "这个就是关键了，默认的算法是 cubic, 也有其他算法可以使用，比如 Google 的 BBR "
				},
				{
					"Type": "NodeSup",
					"Data": "sup",
					"Children": [
						{
							"Type": "NodeSupOpenMarker"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeText",
							"Data": "[3]"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeSupCloseMarker"
						}
					]
				},
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": " ."
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-73btuaz",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-73btuaz"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "主要的逻辑是，慢启动(Slow start), 发送数据来测试，如果能正确收到 receiver 那边的 ack，说明当前网络能容纳这个吞吐，将 cwnd x 2，然后继续测试。直到下面一种情况发生："
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-jtxxpb4",
			"Type": "NodeList",
			"ListData": {
				"Typ": 1
			},
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-jtxxpb4"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"ID": "20220901143215-3k0dy6a",
					"Type": "NodeListItem",
					"ListData": {
						"Typ": 1,
						"Delimiter": 46,
						"Marker": "MS4=",
						"Num": 1
					},
					"Properties": {
						"id": "20220901143215-3k0dy6a"
					},
					"Children": [
						{
							"ID": "20220901143215-8i6wchh",
							"Type": "NodeParagraph",
							"Properties": {
								"id": "20220901143215-8i6wchh"
							},
							"Children": [
								{
									"Type": "NodeText",
									"Data": "发送的包没有收到 ACK"
								}
							]
						}
					]
				},
				{
					"ID": "20220901143215-uzg1f32",
					"Type": "NodeListItem",
					"ListData": {
						"Typ": 1,
						"Delimiter": 46,
						"Marker": "Mi4=",
						"Num": 2
					},
					"Properties": {
						"id": "20220901143215-uzg1f32"
					},
					"Children": [
						{
							"ID": "20220901143215-pregss4",
							"Type": "NodeParagraph",
							"Properties": {
								"id": "20220901143215-pregss4"
							},
							"Children": [
								{
									"Type": "NodeText",
									"Data": "cwnd 已经等于 rwnd 了"
								}
							]
						}
					]
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-iu48td1",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-iu48td1"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "第 2 点很好理解，说明网络吞吐并不是一个瓶颈，瓶颈是在接收端的 buffer 不够大。cwnd 不能超过 rwnd，不然会 overload 接收端。"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-yywipx5",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-yywipx5"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "对于第 1 点，本质上，发送端是用丢包来检测网络状况的，如果没有发生丢包，表示一切正常，如果发生丢包，说明网络处理不了这个发送速度，这时候发送端会直接将 cwnd 减半。"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-w2sf5fe",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-w2sf5fe"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "但实际造成第 1 点的情况并不一定是网络吞吐瓶颈，而可能是以下几种情况："
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-6grliid",
			"Type": "NodeList",
			"ListData": {
				"Typ": 1
			},
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-6grliid"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"ID": "20220901143215-lgt5z2b",
					"Type": "NodeListItem",
					"ListData": {
						"Typ": 1,
						"Delimiter": 46,
						"Marker": "MS4=",
						"Num": 1
					},
					"Properties": {
						"id": "20220901143215-lgt5z2b"
					},
					"Children": [
						{
							"ID": "20220901143215-1zmeolh",
							"Type": "NodeParagraph",
							"Properties": {
								"id": "20220901143215-1zmeolh"
							},
							"Children": [
								{
									"Type": "NodeText",
									"Data": "网络达到了瓶颈"
								}
							]
						}
					]
				},
				{
					"ID": "20220901143215-h0f02vj",
					"Type": "NodeListItem",
					"ListData": {
						"Typ": 1,
						"Delimiter": 46,
						"Marker": "Mi4=",
						"Num": 2
					},
					"Properties": {
						"id": "20220901143215-h0f02vj"
					},
					"Children": [
						{
							"ID": "20220901143215-bvf63tp",
							"Type": "NodeParagraph",
							"Properties": {
								"id": "20220901143215-bvf63tp"
							},
							"Children": [
								{
									"Type": "NodeText",
									"Data": "网络质量问题丢包"
								}
							]
						}
					]
				},
				{
					"ID": "20220901143215-iaiz4or",
					"Type": "NodeListItem",
					"ListData": {
						"Typ": 1,
						"Delimiter": 46,
						"Marker": "My4=",
						"Num": 3
					},
					"Properties": {
						"id": "20220901143215-iaiz4or"
					},
					"Children": [
						{
							"ID": "20220901143215-i0cr16a",
							"Type": "NodeParagraph",
							"Properties": {
								"id": "20220901143215-i0cr16a"
							},
							"Children": [
								{
									"Type": "NodeText",
									"Data": "中间网络设备延迟了包的送达，导致发送端没有在预期时间内收到 ACK"
								}
							]
						}
					]
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-fs6bph7",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-fs6bph7"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "2 和 3 原因都会造成 cwnd 下降，无法充分利用网络吞吐。"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-465ro0s",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-465ro0s"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "以上就是基本的原理，下面介绍如何定位这种问题。"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-velwi5n",
			"Type": "NodeHeading",
			"HeadingLevel": 2,
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-velwi5n"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "rwnd 查看方式"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-1utsdgb",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-1utsdgb"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "这个 window size 直接就在 TCP header 里面，抓下来就能看这个字段。"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-6c1fe3x",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-6c1fe3x"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeImage",
					"Data": "span",
					"Children": [
						{
							"Type": "NodeBang"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeOpenBracket"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeLinkText",
							"Data": "图片"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeCloseBracket"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeOpenParen"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeLinkDest",
							"Data": "assets/640-20220901143214-mt3ps93"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeCloseParen"
						}
					]
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-ddrwhvg",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-ddrwhvg"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "但是真正的 window size 需要乘以 factor, factor 是在 TCP 握手节点通过 TCP Options 协商的 "
				},
				{
					"Type": "NodeSup",
					"Data": "sup",
					"Children": [
						{
							"Type": "NodeSupOpenMarker"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeText",
							"Data": "[4]"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeSupCloseMarker"
						}
					]
				},
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": " 。所以如果分析一条 TCP 连接的 window size，必须抓到握手阶段的包，不然就不可以知道协商的 factor 是多少。"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-1nflkxb",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-1nflkxb"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeImage",
					"Data": "span",
					"Children": [
						{
							"Type": "NodeBang"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeOpenBracket"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeLinkText",
							"Data": "图片"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeCloseBracket"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeOpenParen"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeLinkDest",
							"Data": "assets/640-20220901143214-sqdih8w"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeCloseParen"
						}
					]
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-f11emzm",
			"Type": "NodeHeading",
			"HeadingLevel": 2,
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-f11emzm"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "cwnd 查看方式"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-lr3njxw",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-lr3njxw"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "Congestion control 是发送端通过算法得到的一个动态变量，会试试调整，并不会体现在协议的传输数据中。所以要看这个，必须在发送端的机器上看。"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-9g23g84",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-9g23g84"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "在 Linux 中可以使用 "
				},
				{
					"Type": "NodeCodeSpan",
					"Data": "code",
					"Children": [
						{
							"Type": "NodeCodeSpanOpenMarker"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeCodeSpanContent",
							"Data": "ss -i"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeCodeSpanCloseMarker"
						}
					]
				},
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": " 选项将 TCP 连接的参数都打印出来。"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-6ap5fwf",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-6ap5fwf"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeImage",
					"Data": "span",
					"Children": [
						{
							"Type": "NodeBang"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeOpenBracket"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeLinkText",
							"Data": "图片"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeCloseBracket"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeOpenParen"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeLinkDest",
							"Data": "assets/640-20220901143214-qgsrwya"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeCloseParen"
						}
					]
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-utcri6m",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-utcri6m"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "这里展示的单位是 TCP MSS."
				},
				{
					"Type": "NodeSup",
					"Data": "sup",
					"Children": [
						{
							"Type": "NodeSupOpenMarker"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeText",
							"Data": "[5]"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeSupCloseMarker"
						}
					]
				},
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": " 即实际大小是 1460bytes * 10."
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-8k11qmx",
			"Type": "NodeHeading",
			"HeadingLevel": 2,
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-8k11qmx"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "Wireshark 分析"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-7djw2of",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-7djw2of"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "Wireshark 提供了非常使用的统计功能，可以让你一眼就能看出当前的瓶颈是发生在了哪里。但是第一次打开这个图我不会看，一脸懵逼，也没查到资料要怎么看。好在我同事 "
				},
				{
					"Type": "NodeSup",
					"Data": "sup",
					"Children": [
						{
							"Type": "NodeSupOpenMarker"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeText",
							"Data": "[6]"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeSupCloseMarker"
						}
					]
				},
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": " 会，他把我教会了，我在这里记录一下，把你也教会。"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-u2l2v23",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-u2l2v23"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "首先，打开的方式如下："
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-bnureh6",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-bnureh6"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeImage",
					"Data": "span",
					"Children": [
						{
							"Type": "NodeBang"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeOpenBracket"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeLinkText",
							"Data": "图片"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeCloseBracket"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeOpenParen"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeLinkDest",
							"Data": "assets/640-20220901143214-r2txb85"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeCloseParen"
						}
					]
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-68a8kga",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-68a8kga"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "然后你会看到如下的图。"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-b6p2hmn",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-b6p2hmn"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeImage",
					"Data": "span",
					"Children": [
						{
							"Type": "NodeBang"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeOpenBracket"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeLinkText",
							"Data": "图片"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeCloseBracket"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeOpenParen"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeLinkDest",
							"Data": "assets/640-20220901143214-wzebzbw"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeCloseParen"
						}
					]
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-r0ivmoy",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-r0ivmoy"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "首先需要明确，tcptrace 的图表示的是单方向的数据发送，因为 tcp 是双工协议，两边都能发送数据。其中最上面写了你当前在看的图数据是从 10.0.0.1 发送到 192.168.0.1 的，然后按右下角的按钮可以切换看的方向。"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-zgyzp29",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-zgyzp29"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "X 轴表示的是时间，很好理解。"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-ivxm45z",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-ivxm45z"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "然后理解一下 Y 轴表示的 Sequence Number, 就是 TCP 包中的 Sequence Number，这个很关键。图中所有的数据，都是以 Sequence Number 为准的。"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-b3ovxca",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-b3ovxca"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "所以，你如果看到如上图所示，那么说明你看反了，因为数据的 Sequence Number 并没有增加过，说明几乎没有发送过数据，需要点击 Switch Direction。"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-kw9oqn5",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-kw9oqn5"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeImage",
					"Data": "span",
					"Children": [
						{
							"Type": "NodeBang"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeOpenBracket"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeLinkText",
							"Data": "图片"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeCloseBracket"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeOpenParen"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeLinkDest",
							"Data": "assets/640-20220901143214-9zty5q2"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeCloseParen"
						}
					]
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-tn0n1oo",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-tn0n1oo"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "这就对了，可以看到我们传输的 Sequence Number 在随着时间增加而增加。"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-vb0nmy4",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-vb0nmy4"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "这里面有 3 条线，含义如下："
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-8isgsxy",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-8isgsxy"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeImage",
					"Data": "span",
					"Children": [
						{
							"Type": "NodeBang"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeOpenBracket"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeLinkText",
							"Data": "图片"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeCloseBracket"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeOpenParen"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeLinkDest",
							"Data": "assets/640-20220901143214-69czmpe"
						},
						{
							"Type": "NodeCloseParen"
						}
					]
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-bbcmcr7",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-bbcmcr7"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "除此之外，另外还有两种线："
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-plr5x3e",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
