		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-to12nns",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-to12nns"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "需要始终记住的是 Y 轴是 Sequence Number，红色的线表示 SACK 的线表示这一段 Sequence Number 我已经收到了，然后配合黄色线表示 ACK 过的 Sequence Number，那么发送端就会知道，在中间这段空挡，包丢了，红色线和黄色线纵向的空白，是没有被 ACK 的包。所以，需要重新传输。而蓝色的线就是表示又重新传输了一遍。"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-x67l89n",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-x67l89n"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "学会了看这些图，我们可以认识几种常见的 pattern："
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-bb441cv",
			"Type": "NodeHeading",
			"HeadingLevel": 3,
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-bb441cv"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "丢包"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20220901143215-bdzrnw3",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20220901143215-bdzrnw3"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeImage",
